OL,7,FA group tasked with helping young
OL,8,Fpeople in Northern Ireland who were
OL,9,Fadopted or who grew up in care find
OL,10,Fanswers about their past, fears it
OL,11,Fwill not get its funding renewed later
OL,12,Fthis year.
