OL,3,CCalls to save adoption service:
OL,4,C'Losing Life Story Project would be a
OL,5,Ctravesty'
OL,7,FAn adoptive parent has told UTV losing
OL,8,Fthe service would be a 'travesty' for
OL,9,Fthose young people who still have yet
OL,10,Fto find out about their past.
OL,12,FPaul Woods said: "There are so many
OL,13,Fchildren and young people who could
OL,14,Fand should be able to avail of the
OL,15,Fexpertise and experience of those who
OL,16,Frun this project.
