OL,3,CCalls to save adoption service:
OL,4,C'Losing Life Story Project would be a
OL,5,Ctravesty'
OL,7,F"For those who need that support, and
OL,8,Fare entitled to that support, it would
OL,9,Fbe travesty for them if that support
OL,10,Fwasn't available because of a funding
OL,11,Fissue. Those children don't deserve
OL,12,Fthat."
OL,14,FSarah Johnston from Life Story Project
OL,15,Ftold UTV the service is a statutory
OL,16,Fright in other parts of the UK.
OL,18,F"Without another funder this service
OL,19,Fwill cease to exist.
